Map Specs

compile time :.........................44 seconds Map size:...............................small to medium Gameplay:..............................LOTS OF FUN!!! detail on map:.........................Not much detail in map but it has crazy gameplay.

Map Description

This map is my firs ever map but i have never uploaded it because the map lacks detail. the skybox attaches to the floor and there is no wall surrounding tha map. inside the buildings there are very few props if any. Just recentley i tried this map out on my CSS: DM server and found that the gameplay is Incredible it is alot of fun. one side of the map terrorists spawn and on the other counter terrorists spawn. they meet in the middle and all hell breaks loose. This map is also good for GunGame . NOTE: I do not know why i called the map "aim_ag_battalion"
